pullRequest.title: [Data Plane Mgr] UT Test Automation - Part III
pullRequest.bodyText:
The third version of DPM Automation UT:

Refactored the old version of UTs
Optimized the logic of automatically generating input and output payload
The verification content of UTs has been changed. The output protobuff was only roughly compared before, and now it can be specific to the value of each line
